The paper discusses improving the robustness of ptychography phase retrieval algorithms against noise, which involves optimization and image processing techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by optimization (cs.Optimization), information theory (cs.IT), multimedia (cs.MM), and numerical analysis (cs.NA).
